13:23.160 --> 13:24.880
In-play betting.

13:24.880 --> 13:26.880
Every corner, every goal,

13:26.880 --> 13:28.680
every free kick - you can bet
on anything these days.

13:28.680 --> 13:30.000
I know what in-play betting is!

13:30.000 --> 13:33.400
Right, so if a betting syndicate
from the Far East, say,

13:33.400 --> 13:36.600
