13:45.280 --> 13:47.200
Are you making an allegation here?

13:47.200 --> 13:48.400
He's talking out of his arse.

13:48.400 --> 13:50.080
It happens all the time in Italy.
In the San Siro...

13:50.080 --> 13:52.960
Oh, will you stop going on
about the shitting San Siro!

13:52.960 --> 13:56.680
You were a backup referee at
an under-14s friendly in 1992!

13:56.680 --> 13:57.800
Under 17s.

13:57.800 --> 14:01.560
