here, we can have this game
abandoned.

14:48.280 --> 14:49.360
It was only a throw-in!

14:50.680 --> 14:52.360
I didn't think it would matter
that much either way.

14:52.360 --> 14:55.440
Oh, my giddy aunt,
I am not hearing this!

14:55.440 --> 14:57.400
I didn't know they were gonna
go and score off the back of
it, did I?

14:57.400 --> 14:58.800
It was a foot and a half in!

14:58.800 --> 15:00.040
I panicked!

15:00.040 --> 15:02.640
They said if I didn't comply,
something bad would happen to me.

15:02.640 --> 15:04.240
What, they'd unplug the
vending machines?

15:04.240 --> 15:07.560
Martin, please.
It's your last-ever game.

15:07.560 --> 15:09.080
I'll split the money with you.

15:09.080 --> 15:11.280
I-I-I'll give it to charity.

15:11.280 --> 15:12.840
Just don't dob me in it,
please!

15:12.840 --> 15:14.000
Just let me think, will you?

15:14.000 --> 15:16.120
Why did you do it, Oggy?

15:17.240 --> 15:20.040
We get treated like shit
week in, week out.

15:20.040 --> 15:22.760
Spat at by so-called fans,

15:22.760 --> 15:24.480
abused by players, managers,

15:24.480 --> 15:26.440
then the pundits weigh in
and...

15:27.680 --> 15:30.600
..suddenly your kids
are getting bullied at school.

15:30.600 --> 15:32.840
That's no excuse, Oggy.

15:32.840 --> 15:34.040
DOOR OPENS

15:34.040 --> 15:35.880
What the fuck is going on
with you lot today?

15:35.880 --> 15:38.400
Have you seen this footage?
Calvin, you cannot be in here!

15:38.400 --> 15:42.000
There's no way that that's over
the line. Look. Look!

15:42.000 --> 15:43.720
We're not permitted to see that
footage until after the game.

15:43.720 --> 15:46.320
Are you kidding me, Martin?
Are you fucking

15:46.320 --> 15:47.800
