Please, Calvin.

15:47.800 --> 15:50.160
MITCH: Where is he? Where
is he?!

15:52.480 --> 15:54.640
I'll rip his fucking head off!

15:54.640 --> 15:55.800
Mitchell, out! Linesman?!

15:55.800 --> 15:57.960
Call yourself a linesman?
Have you seen that?

15:57.960 --> 15:59.440
You could drive a fuckin' bus
through that gap!

15:59.440 --> 16:00.920
Martin, you have to say
something! Come on, man!

16:00.920 --> 16:02.320
At least send him out there
to apologise.

16:02.320 --> 16:04.880
Oh, what, so I can have food
thrown in me face again?

16:04.880 --> 16:06.200
Oh, you'd enjoy that, wouldn't
you?

16:06.200 --> 16:07.560
You'd eat it, you fat git!

16:07.560 --> 16:09.520
Say that again, you...

16:09.520 --> 16:12.360
ALL YELLING
Say it to my face!

16:12.360 --> 16:14.080
Go on, say it again!

16:14.080 --> 16:16.000
Go on!

16:16.000 --> 16:18.840
THUMP
WHISTLE BLOWS

16:22.240 --> 16:23.440
What are you doing?

16:24.720 --> 16:28.000
You're off!
You're out the game!

16:28.000 --> 16:29.080
You can't do that!

16:29.080 --> 16:31.360
You can't do that.
He can't do that, it's half-time!

16:31.360 --> 16:33.480
Course he can.
Brendan, tell him!

16:33.480 --> 16:36.760
Law 12. The referee
has the authority to
take disciplinary action

16:36.760 --> 16:39.160
from entering the field of play
for the pre-match inspection

16:39.160 --> 16:41.160
until leaving the field of play
at the end of the match.

16:41.160 --> 16:43.000
This is a conspiracy!

16:43.000 --> 16:46.280
You should be whipped, the
lot of you! Martin, you can't.

16:47.320 --> 16:49.880
If I meant to show him the yellow
card, I can change my mind, can't I?

16:49.880 --> 16:52.480
You've already booked him once,
Martin, it's a dismissal either way.

16:52.480 --> 16:54.320
I want him red-carded -
violent conduct!

16:54.320 --> 16:57.040
Yeah? Well, it's nothing to do
with you, is it, knobhead?!

16:57.040 --> 16:58.320
Get him out of here!

17:00.880 --> 17:02.160
Get my head!

17:10.560 --> 17:11.920
Martin, you can't...

17:13.560 --> 17:15.680
Not in this match, not today.
Please!

17:15.680 --> 17:17.480
Well, I'm sorry, Calvin.
It's the laws of the game.

17:17.480 --> 17:19.440
So, you know,
it's a straight red.

17:19.440 --> 17:21.360
A straight red?

17:21.360 --> 17:22.600
Mm-hm.

17:24.680 --> 17:27.000
Well, that's the only straight
thing about you, then, isn't it?

17:31.640 --> 17:34.640
You've sucked my cock for the last
time, Martin, do you understand?

17:34.640 --> 17:36.000
You're pathetic.

17:37.480 --> 17:39.520
Don't call me again!

17:46.320 --> 17:47.600
