The referee's a wanker!

18:09.720 --> 18:11.840
I'll put all that
in the report, or...?

18:16.520 --> 18:19.680
Just put Number 9, Cooke,
dismissed for violent conduct.

18:25.760 --> 18:27.840
Martin...
Don't.

18:29.280 --> 18:31.360
