18:35.160 --> 18:39.120
What are we going to do
about... the other thing?

18:43.200 --> 18:46.080
Did you report that approach
to the FA, Phil?

18:46.080 --> 18:47.520
Course not.

18:47.520 --> 18:49.760
I was scared of ruining my
chances for the World Cup.

18:49.760 --> 18:51.640
