18:54.920 --> 18:56.360
Oh, Martin, I don't think...

18:56.360 --> 19:00.000
If the opportunity comes to give
United a goal, I'm going to take it,

19:00.000 --> 19:02.200
be it an offside or a penalty
or whatever,

19:02.200 --> 19:05.360
and I want you lot to back me
up. Do you understand?

19:05.360 --> 19:07.640
It's just about being fair
and proper.

19:07.640 --> 19:10.600
Sorry, but how is that fair
and proper?

19:10.600 --> 19:12.320
If he hadn't awarded that
throw-in to Rovers,

19:12.320 --> 19:14.160
they wouldn't have scored and it
would have been 0-0,
wouldn't it?

19:14.160 --> 19:16.000
So we're just evening things
up.

19:16.000 --> 19:18.000
Whoever wins after that,
well, good luck to them.

19:18.000 --> 19:21.560
This is...highly irregular,
Martin.

19:21.560 --> 19:23.000
Are you're sure that...

19:23.000 --> 19:25.400
..your judgment hasn't been
coloured by...

19:25.400 --> 19:26.800
..you know?

19:29.120 --> 19:30.280
