19:32.200 --> 19:33.800
Calvin.

19:33.800 --> 19:35.120
The fact you just suc...

19:35.120 --> 19:36.400
Sent him off.

19:37.840 --> 19:39.800
I've done nothing wrong.

19:41.880 --> 19:44.520
My whole career has been
above board and by the book.

19:44.520 --> 19:46.920
Yet you're about to gift a goal
to United.

19:46.920 --> 19:48.520
My conscience is clear.

19:50.040 --> 19:53.120
Now, if any of you want to report
what's happened and go to the FA,

19:53.120 --> 19:55.400
then say so now

19:55.400 --> 19:57.600
and we'll stop this game.

19:57.600 --> 19:59.120
Hm? Well?

20:04.440 --> 20:07.040
