about earlier, you know.

26:10.040 --> 26:12.520
Things were said
in the heat of the moment.

26:12.520 --> 26:15.240
There's no hard feelings,
Mitch, eh? I understand.

26:15.240 --> 26:17.640
Get carried away, we do,
don't we, eh?

26:17.640 --> 26:20.440
About 22 blokes chasing a
pig's bladder around a field.

26:20.440 --> 26:23.520
Well, the game's nothing without
passion and we should never
apologise for that.

26:23.520 --> 26:24.560
Thanks. Er...

26:24.560 --> 26:26.800
