with press out there

26:29.400 --> 26:31.240
and they all want to talk
to you.

26:31.240 --> 26:33.880
They're saying all sorts of
nonsense about you and young Calvin.

26:33.880 --> 26:35.520
I don't believe a word of it,
mind you, now,

26:35.520 --> 26:38.120
but when you leave, you know, you
ought to use the back entrance.

26:38.120 --> 26:39.840
Exit.

26:39.840 --> 26:41.360
That's the one. Not the...

26:41.360 --> 26:42.760
All right.

26:42.760 --> 26:44.200
Oh, er, hey!

26:44.200 --> 26:45.920
You're a City fan, aren't you?

26:45.920 --> 26:49.000
Er, yeah, yeah, for my sins.

26:49.000 --> 26:51.800
Well, if it's any consolation,
you had a good win today,
you know, Preston.

26:51.800 --> 26:54.960
3-1.
Oh, well. Every cloud, eh?

26:54.960 --> 26:56.800
They've also said
they're gonna dock us points,

26:56.800 --> 26:59.120
by the look of things,
because of all the fracas.

26:59.120 --> 27:01.120
Oh, you think so?
Well, you saw it out there.

27:01.120 --> 27:02.640
I mean, it was brutal.

27:02.640 --> 27:04.880
They're already calling it
"The War of Wallis Park".

27:04.880 --> 27:08.200
Gary Lineker, he's been on
Twitter saying that it
would be morally wrong

27:08.200 --> 27:09.720
if we were promoted.

27:09.720 --> 27:11.480
Yeah, but he's into refugees
and all that malarkey.

27:11.480 --> 27:12.760
So he shouldn't be listened
to, really.

27:12.760 --> 27:14.120
He's an interfering do-gooder.

27:14.120 --> 27:16.800
Yeah. Never professionally
booked, though, eh? That
takes some restraint.

27:16.800 --> 27:18.560
You know what that means, though,
don't you? We get docked

27:18.560 --> 27:20.640
and we're gonna go down
to third place.

27:20.640 --> 27:22.160
And that means you lot, City,

27:22.160 --> 27:24.440
you're gonna get promoted
instead of us, you know?

27:24.440 --> 27:26.400
£150 million quid right up
the shitter!

27:26.400 --> 27:27.800
No offence.

27:27.800 --> 27:29.360
